{"tid":1754993,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想換通風好嘅機箱同CPU Cooler","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T22:41:06.000Z","uid":41727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bae873ebd786b3955c42a2f8d670f3861fe64cb2","tid":1754993,"uid":41727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"本身用開個Cooler Master靜音機箱(唔記得型號), 前面兩把12cm跟機箱嘅風扇入風, CPU Cooler就用開Antec Kuhler H20 620, 水冷排裝喺機箱尾出風位(12cm風扇), 打機嗰陣試過見到CPU上到100度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> GPU都上到80度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但受機箱限制冇位再加風扇, CPU Cooler亦冇空間換隻大舊啲嘅款, 所以把心一橫想換晒機箱同CPU Cooler, 同埋可能再加啲風扇, 求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機箱要求：<br />\n通風好好, 防塵, 要有3個或以上3.5&quot;HDD位置, 無須光碟機, 無須靜音<br />\n<br />\nCPU Cooler要求：<br />\n想轉風冷唔用水冷, 鍾意貓頭鷹牌, 見唔少人推介 U12, 但想問下D14, D15屌唔屌得過? 換左機箱應該有空間裝呢啲大舊款"},{"pid":"dfbd1959e2f5c0e515f602f3c4a6fbff03906360","tid":1754993,"uid":146525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"Silverstone Raven系列通風一流<br />\n加埋D15，又靜又凍<br />\n<br />\n利申用緊D14加rv02"},{"pid":"bd1f0abf4b2e328ae2fc12c3bbe58aacb8423fd2","tid":1754993,"uid":41727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbd1959e2f5c0e515f602f3c4a6fbff03906360","tid":1754993,"uid":146525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"Silverstone Raven系列通風一流<br />\n加埋D15，又靜又凍<br />\n<br />\n利申用緊D14加rv02"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"RV02 用落會唔會好吸塵? 同埋佢好多光碟機空間, 現代已經唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢個設計搞到部機好長, 仲長過我張檯......Research過下原來呢條line已經幾年冇出新款, 所以啲配置都out out地"},{"pid":"8d6b4b8c730b2dd4b5f4fcfb0a3654b585c56516","tid":1754993,"uid":146525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd1f0abf4b2e328ae2fc12c3bbe58aacb8423fd2","tid":1754993,"uid":41727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"